    "description": "Juicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Digital Marketing Manager at our Bengaluru location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Juicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates:\nJuicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Juicy Chemistry Asia Pacific Associates!",
